  <brief_title>Assessment of Spontaneous Baroreflex Sensitivity in Carriers of Implantable Cardioverter Defibrillators: Association With Disorders of the Ventricular Heart Rate. Case-control Study</brief_title>
  <acronym>BARODEF</acronym>
  <sponsors>
